title: U2 - The Ultimate MP3 Collection (by Entropy) - UPDATE 1
description:
This is an Update to the previously released U2 collection.  The mps files were either ripped from CD or downloaded from U2.com (in the case of the digital bonus material.  Everything is tagged with appropriate artwork.  I have included Rattle and Hum, since it was somehow not included in the first torrent.  If you are a new collector, this torrent in addition to the previously released MP3 torrent should give you every version of every song that has ever been commercially released.  I hope you enjoy it.  A FLAC version will be coming soon.  As always, if you like the music, buy the albums.  Great artists deserve our financial support.
